# Code Style & Formatting

## 1. Linting & Formatting
- Use **Ruff** for linting and auto-fixes:
  ```bash
  ruff check . --fix
Use mypy for static type checking.

## 2. Ruff Configuration
Ensure Ruff is installed in every project:
bash
